'''奥朗日凯旋门'''（{{lang-fr|Arc de triomphe d'Orange}}）是一个[[凯旋门|凯旋门]]，位于法国东南部城市[[奥朗日|奥朗日]]。关于凯旋门何时建成尚有争议<ref>Bibliography of scholarship that rejects the inscription as evidence for dating the construction is presented by James C. Anderson, Jr., "Anachronism in the Roman Architecture of Gaul: The Date of the Maison Carrée at Nîmes" ''The Journal of the Society of Architectural Historians'' '''60''',1（March 2001:68-79）  p. 71 note 12; Anderson offers a revised date in the first half of the second century for the [[Maison_Carrée|Maison Carrée]]: "in short, once the date of the Maison Carrée is called into question, the entire chronology for such Romano-Provençal monuments requires reassessment"（p. 72）.</ref>，目前的研究接受作为证据的铭文<ref>The traditional dating for the triumphal arches of [[纳博讷高卢|Gallia Narbonensis]] is summarized in Pierre Gros, "Pour une chronologie des arcs de triomphe de Gaule narbonnaise", ''Gallia'' '''37'''（1979:55-83</ref>支持建于[[奥古斯都|奥古斯都]]在位期间的说法<ref name="Cleere"/>。它修建在过去的阿格里帕大道（via Agrippa）上，褒扬[[高卢战争|高卢战争]]和第二奥古斯都军团的退伍军人。后来由皇帝[[提庇留|提庇留]]重建，以庆祝日耳曼尼库斯战胜[[莱茵兰|莱茵兰]]的日耳曼部落<ref name="Cleere"/>。凯旋门内有公元27年献给皇帝提庇留的铭文<ref name="Bromwich">{{cite book
  | last = Bromwich
  | first = James
  | title = The Roman Remains of Southern France: A Guidebook
  | url = https://archive.org/details/romanremainsofso0000brom
  | publisher = Routledge
  | date = 1993
  | pages = [https://archive.org/details/romanremainsofso0000brom/page/183 183]–186
  | isbn = 0415143586 }}
</ref>。凯旋门描绘各种军事主题的浮雕，包括海战，以及与[[日耳曼人|日耳曼人]]和[[高卢人|高卢人]]的战争<ref name="Bromwich"/>。

在中世纪，这座凯旋门被修建到城墙内，以守卫城市的北部入口<ref name="Cleere">{{cite book
  | last = Cleere
  | first = Henry
  | title = Southern France: An Oxford Archaeological Guide 
  | url = https://archive.org/details/southernfranceox0000clee
  | publisher = Oxford University Press
  | date = May 14, 2001
  | pages = [https://archive.org/details/southernfranceox0000clee/page/122 122]–123
  | isbn = 0192880063 }}
</ref>。建筑师奥古斯丁Caristie进行研究，在1850年代进行修复<ref name="Bromwich"/>。凯旋门最初使用巨大的石灰石块建造。它有三个拱门，中间一个大于侧翼的。整个建筑长19.57米，宽8.40米，高19.21米<ref name="Cleere"/>。每个立面有四个[[科林斯柱式|科林斯柱]]。这座凯旋门是幸存下来最古老的凯旋门，其设计后来为罗马城的[[塞维鲁凯旋门|塞维鲁凯旋门]]和[[君士坦丁凯旋门|君士坦丁凯旋门]]所效仿。

